{"tid":2293034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊巴送禮畀隊友 人人一部PS5","createTime":"2020-11-20T03:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T11:47:40.000Z","uid":10338,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"084636167d0b272157ed86b0934219d9cae6357d","tid":2293034,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:26:05.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】AC米蘭老將伊巴謙莫域果然有大哥風範，為每位隊友送一部電子遊戲機。<br />\n日本電子遊戲機PS5近日在意大利推出發售，所有AC米蘭球員已經每人得到一部，這並非由該公司贈送，而是39歲老將伊巴謙莫域（Zlatan Ibrahimovic）送出的禮物。阿根廷球員梅沙基奧和西班牙前鋒卡斯迪耶荷分別在社交網站上載圖片，向伊巴致謝。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴重返AC米蘭展開第二春，今季表現更是冠絕全隊，5場聯賽射入8球和1個助攻，目前更排在意甲射手榜首位。既然是球隊的領袖人物，伊巴自然要懂得刺激士氣。<br />\n<br />\n排在意甲榜首的AC米蘭，本輪聯賽將作客聯賽第3位的拿玻里，一旦落敗或要交出「一哥」地位，希望伊巴的禮物能協助球隊全取3分。"},{"pid":"f1cfba72efc59318b4350295c9f64c67d510567e","tid":2293034,"uid":6310,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"啲霸氣勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78dcd54f92ba71975342aee3ac85f4cd57edf5c","tid":2293034,"uid":154872,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"Pro Club練戰術同走位"},{"pid":"5d6fcaa09a89081b85966026b0185697674e7ce4","tid":2293034,"uid":53672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:39:17.000Z","msg":"大佬伊巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd4bc7d2a899c354f8eabdbb639dfa58fae42c0","tid":2293034,"uid":221571,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"點解買到咁多部<br />\n係咪有特權<br />\n係咪大撚哂<br />\n！！！"},{"pid":"7c5280f921082e433be2490987f7dec1a8a4d5c8","tid":2293034,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T03:46:43.000Z","msg":"一齊開pro club練波"},{"pid":"9f598216021ec285e8daca108fa0ae57a3766a7b","tid":2293034,"uid":64636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"